WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:20.850 align:middle line:90%


00:00:20.850 --> 00:00:23.162 align:middle line:84%
>>So there I was
sitting in front of him

00:00:23.162 --> 00:00:27.580 align:middle line:84%
at what was to be
my last darshan.

00:00:27.580 --> 00:00:30.490 align:middle line:84%
Right after this, I was going
to get on a bus or train

00:00:30.490 --> 00:00:33.980 align:middle line:84%
and go up to Delhi, and catch
the plane back to the States.

00:00:33.980 --> 00:00:35.630 align:middle line:84%
I've been walking
around barefoot

00:00:35.630 --> 00:00:38.652 align:middle line:84%
in a red dress for
about a year and a half.

00:00:38.652 --> 00:00:43.660 align:middle line:90%
And I had no clue what to do.

00:00:43.660 --> 00:00:44.300 align:middle line:90%
Time to go.

00:00:44.300 --> 00:00:46.260 align:middle line:90%
I had to get up.

00:00:46.260 --> 00:00:47.470 align:middle line:90%
I bowed to him.

00:00:47.470 --> 00:00:49.910 align:middle line:90%
I walked across the courtyard.

00:00:49.910 --> 00:00:52.460 align:middle line:84%
And I looked at him
again, looked back at him.

00:00:52.460 --> 00:00:53.580 align:middle line:90%
And I bowed down.

00:00:53.580 --> 00:00:57.950 align:middle line:84%
And then, in my head, I heard
the words, in my own voice,

00:00:57.950 --> 00:01:00.055 align:middle line:84%
even though it
wasn't me saying it.

00:01:00.055 --> 00:01:02.610 align:middle line:90%
It's wasn't like, oh, OK.

00:01:02.610 --> 00:01:08.399 align:middle line:84%
I heard the words "I'll
sing to you in America."

00:01:08.399 --> 00:01:10.387 align:middle line:90%
Right.

00:01:10.387 --> 00:01:11.878 align:middle line:90%
And then I left.

00:01:11.878 --> 00:01:16.848 align:middle line:90%
