00:01:57.452 --> 00:02:01.940 align:middle line:90%


00:02:01.940 --> 00:02:05.750 align:middle line:10%
>>In the '70s, it
was inconceivable

00:02:05.750 --> 00:02:07.250 align:middle line:10%
