00:02:17.260 --> 00:02:20.160 align:middle line:10%
And maybe there were 20 people.

00:02:20.160 --> 00:02:22.830 align:middle line:10%
Then there were 30 people.

00:02:22.830 --> 00:02:28.030 align:middle line:10%
You know, and now, for it
to be a thing, you know,

00:02:28.030 --> 00:02:29.230 align:middle line:10%
is quite startling.

00:02:29.230 --> 00:02:34.655 align:middle line:10%
>>He's really like the Rumi or
the kirtan wallah of our time.

00:02:34.655 --> 00:02:38.280 align:middle line:10%
