00:03:17.600 --> 00:03:18.280 align:middle line:90%
Just enough.

00:03:18.280 --> 00:03:23.210 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC - "OM, NAMAH SHIVAYA"]

00:03:23.210 --> 00:03:27.047 align:middle line:90%


00:03:27.047 --> 00:03:28.505 align:middle line:84%
It's not really
the music business,

00:03:28.505 --> 00:03:31.030 align:middle line:84%
