out and we tour.

00:03:31.030 --> 00:03:32.420 align:middle line:90%
It's not a career.

00:03:32.420 --> 00:03:34.080 align:middle line:90%
It's just my life.

00:03:34.080 --> 00:03:35.280 align:middle line:90%
It's my path.

00:03:35.280 --> 00:03:38.640 align:middle line:90%
It's my practice.

00:03:38.640 --> 00:03:40.720 align:middle line:10%
>>People get born to his music.

