00:04:08.800 --> 00:04:17.260 align:middle line:84%
>>Most singers singing to the
audience, they just, just sing.

00:04:17.260 --> 00:04:20.246 align:middle line:10%
He wants to sing
only to Maharaji.

00:04:20.246 --> 00:04:24.030 align:middle line:90%


00:04:24.030 --> 00:04:30.910 align:middle line:10%
