00:04:36.679 --> 00:04:40.972 align:middle line:90%


00:04:40.972 --> 00:04:43.631 align:middle line:84%
When I realized
if I didn't sing,

00:04:43.631 --> 00:04:48.140 align:middle line:84%
I would never ever
be able to clean out

00:04:48.140 --> 00:04:51.510 align:middle line:90%
the dark places in my own heart.

00:04:51.510 --> 00:04:57.830 align:middle line:84%
The weight of my
unhappiness and my failure

00:04:57.830 --> 00:05:02.840 align:middle line:84%
to find anything in life
other than Maharaji, which,

00:05:02.840 --> 00:05:07.730 align:middle line:84%
I thought, I had
lost when he died.

00:05:07.730 --> 00:05:09.443 align:middle line:90%
I just wasn't going to make it.

00:05:09.443 --> 00:05:13.635 align:middle line:84%
I didn't have it, I
didn't have it in me.

00:05:13.635 --> 00:05:16.792 align:middle line:84%
The only chance I had
was to sing with people.

00:05:16.792 --> 00:05:20.060 align:middle line:90%
