00:05:20.060 --> 00:05:21.985 align:middle line:84%
So I think most of
you know how it works.

00:05:21.985 --> 00:05:25.580 align:middle line:90%


00:05:25.580 --> 00:05:29.500 align:middle line:84%
I sing the line,
and then you sing

00:05:29.500 --> 00:05:32.120 align:middle line:84%
