00:08:06.580 --> 00:08:07.105 align:middle line:90%
>>That day?

00:08:07.105 --> 00:08:07.604 align:middle line:90%
>>Yeah.

00:08:07.604 --> 00:08:08.410 align:middle line:90%
>>There you go.

00:08:08.410 --> 00:08:09.380 align:middle line:90%
>>I was doing ballet.

00:08:09.380 --> 00:08:11.586 align:middle line:84%
