back out of the room.

00:44:05.490 --> 00:44:09.000 align:middle line:84%
And he turned and
he pointed at me

00:44:09.000 --> 00:44:12.710 align:middle line:84%
and he said, promise me
now you'll give up cocaine.

00:44:12.710 --> 00:44:14.100 align:middle line:90%
Promise me now!

00:44:14.100 --> 00:44:18.000 align:middle line:84%
And this guy, you have
no idea about this guy.

00:44:18.000 --> 00:44:21.805 align:middle line:84%
