00:57:09.710 --> 00:57:12.480 align:middle line:90%


00:57:12.480 --> 00:57:14.400 align:middle line:90%
So I quit.

00:57:14.400 --> 00:57:15.510 align:middle line:90%
I quit.

00:57:15.510 --> 00:57:18.370 align:middle line:90%
And I went to India.

00:57:18.370 --> 00:57:22.200 align:middle line:10%
I knew that Maharaji
was the only one who

00:57:22.200 --> 00:57:24.670 align:middle line:10%
could change what
was in my heart.

00:57:24.670 --> 00:57:28.450 align:middle line:10%
And then, if I was going to
continue to sing at all again,

00:57:28.450 --> 00:57:31.160 align:middle line:10%
he was going to do
something, even though he

00:57:31.160 --> 00:57:35.740 align:middle line:10%
had left his body 20 years
already at this point.

00:57:35.740 --> 00:57:40.100 align:middle line:84%
We went to Kainchi
to see Siddhi Ma.

00:57:40.100 --> 00:57:42.670 align:middle line:84%
And Ma said to me,
what are your plans?

00:57:42.670 --> 00:57:45.580 align:middle line:84%
And I said, well, i have
to be back in New York

00:57:45.580 --> 00:57:48.350 align:middle line:90%
by the end of May.

00:57:48.350 --> 00:57:49.355 align:middle line:90%
You she just stopped.

00:57:49.355 --> 00:57:51.930 align:middle line:90%


00:57:51.930 --> 00:57:56.690 align:middle line:84%
And then she said, no, you
have to stay until June 15,

00:57:56.690 --> 00:58:00.700 align:middle line:84%
until the Bhandara at
Kainchi, the celebration

00:58:00.700 --> 00:58:04.600 align:middle line:90%
of the opening of the temple.

00:58:04.600 --> 00:58:06.365 align:middle line:84%
You have to see
Maharaji's big form.

00:58:06.365 --> 00:58:09.544 align:middle line:90%


00:58:09.544 --> 00:58:11.690 align:middle line:90%
I thought, Maharaji's big form?

00:58:11.690 --> 00:58:13.340 align:middle line:90%
What is she talking about?

00:58:13.340 --> 00:58:15.327 align:middle line:84%
But she asked me
to stay, I'll stay.

00:58:15.327 --> 00:58:17.160 align:middle line:84%
And every day, I was
singing with the kirtan

00:58:17.160 --> 00:58:18.590 align:middle line:90%
wallahs for many hours.

00:58:18.590 --> 00:58:19.420 align:middle line:90%
And it was good.

00:58:19.420 --> 00:58:23.280 align:middle line:84%
But still, I knew, nothing
had changed in my heart.

00:58:23.280 --> 00:58:24.840 align:middle line:84%
And so the night
before the Bhandara,

00:58:24.840 --> 00:58:26.792 align:middle line:84%
that night I looked
up at the stars

00:58:26.792 --> 00:58:28.000 align:middle line:90%
and I started talking to him.

00:58:28.000 --> 00:58:31.240 align:middle line:84%
And I said, you haven't
changed anything.

00:58:31.240 --> 00:58:34.050 align:middle line:90%
I don't understand why not.

00:58:34.050 --> 00:58:38.681 align:middle line:84%
Then I said, well, I can't make
you do it if you don't want to.

00:58:38.681 --> 00:58:40.410 align:middle line:90%
What am I going to do?

00:58:40.410 --> 00:58:41.470 align:middle line:90%
I'll go back, I'll sing.

00:58:41.470 --> 00:58:43.850 align:middle line:90%
How bad could it be?

00:58:43.850 --> 00:58:46.216 align:middle line:84%
So the next day was the
day of the Bhandara.

00:58:46.216 --> 00:58:48.950 align:middle line:90%


00:58:48.950 --> 00:58:52.340 align:middle line:84%
This is the day when
50,000-60,000-70,000 people

00:58:52.340 --> 00:58:54.270 align:middle line:90%
come from all over India.

00:58:54.270 --> 00:58:58.260 align:middle line:84%
And they come to be fed, to
take this meal of blessed food,

00:58:58.260 --> 00:58:59.240 align:middle line:90%
of prasad.

00:58:59.240 --> 00:59:02.050 align:middle line:84%
And they line up on
the street for miles.

00:59:02.050 --> 00:59:05.289 align:middle line:84%
The roads closed,
no buses, no cars.

00:59:05.289 --> 00:59:06.696 align:middle line:90%
It's amazing, huh?

