01:00:23.732 --> 01:00:25.440 align:middle line:84%
And then I was actually
feeling peaceful.

01:00:25.440 --> 01:00:28.510 align:middle line:90%


01:00:28.510 --> 01:00:32.320 align:middle line:84%
This was a feeling that I didn't
have much familiarity with.

01:00:32.320 --> 01:00:35.750 align:middle line:90%


01:00:35.750 --> 01:00:41.500 align:middle line:84%
And it was kind of just
spreading through me quietly.

01:00:41.500 --> 01:00:43.830 align:middle line:84%
I was just watching
these people come and go,

01:00:43.830 --> 01:00:48.090 align:middle line:84%
and it reminded me of this
part of the Bhagavad Gita,

01:00:48.090 --> 01:00:51.590 align:middle line:84%
where Krishna shows
Arjuna his divine form.

01:00:51.590 --> 01:00:55.730 align:middle line:84%
And Arjuna looks and he sees all
beings entering into Krishna,

01:00:55.730 --> 01:00:59.792 align:middle line:84%
and all beings leaving Krishna,
and the cycle of incarnation

01:00:59.792 --> 01:01:01.410 align:middle line:90%
on Earth.

01:01:01.410 --> 01:01:06.160 align:middle line:84%
And Krishna says, i come as
time, the great destroyer,

01:01:06.160 --> 01:01:09.750 align:middle line:84%
but at the same time, nothing's
moving it the Universe.

01:01:09.750 --> 01:01:12.330 align:middle line:90%
There's perfect stillness.

01:01:12.330 --> 01:01:15.640 align:middle line:84%
It was like another
level opening up

01:01:15.640 --> 01:01:21.420 align:middle line:84%
on top of this regular
level of seeing things.

01:01:21.420 --> 01:01:23.250 align:middle line:84%
I went to sit behind
the Durga temple,

01:01:23.250 --> 01:01:26.670 align:middle line:84%
where Maharaji had made
me the pujari there back

01:01:26.670 --> 01:01:28.300 align:middle line:90%
in the old days.

01:01:28.300 --> 01:01:31.280 align:middle line:84%
And I leaned up
against the temple

01:01:31.280 --> 01:01:32.970 align:middle line:90%
and I just closed my eyes.

01:01:32.970 --> 01:01:36.980 align:middle line:84%
The next thing I knew,
I was coming back.

01:01:36.980 --> 01:01:42.050 align:middle line:84%
And I have no idea how long I'd
been sitting there, no idea.

01:01:42.050 --> 01:01:50.780 align:middle line:84%
But I was now fully,
deeply, and completely

01:01:50.780 --> 01:01:55.390 align:middle line:84%
in the state of
peaceful presence.

01:01:55.390 --> 01:01:59.410 align:middle line:84%
This vast space,
outside of which

01:01:59.410 --> 01:02:03.940 align:middle line:84%
there could not be anything,
like the clouds in the sky,

01:02:03.940 --> 01:02:08.130 align:middle line:84%
like the Earth, like
everything is held in space.

01:02:08.130 --> 01:02:15.523 align:middle line:84%
And I wasn't there who I
knew myself as was not there

01:02:15.523 --> 01:02:16.250 align:middle line:90%
any more.

01:02:16.250 --> 01:02:18.430 align:middle line:90%
And I was just present.

01:02:18.430 --> 01:02:23.250 align:middle line:84%
And I felt as if I had
like a wave in the ocean.

01:02:23.250 --> 01:02:27.370 align:middle line:84%
Ocean and wave
are not different.

01:02:27.370 --> 01:02:30.800 align:middle line:84%
They appear different
at certain times,

01:02:30.800 --> 01:02:34.390 align:middle line:84%
because certain forces
cause the wave to be formed.

01:02:34.390 --> 01:02:36.595 align:middle line:84%
The wave must think it's
really great, right?

01:02:36.595 --> 01:02:39.170 align:middle line:90%
And then it dissolves.

01:02:39.170 --> 01:02:43.600 align:middle line:84%
Why bother to get all puffed
up with all that shit?

01:02:43.600 --> 01:02:45.670 align:middle line:84%
You're going to dissolves,
sooner or later,

01:02:45.670 --> 01:02:48.690 align:middle line:90%
it makes no difference.

01:02:48.690 --> 01:02:51.380 align:middle line:84%
It's temporary, don't
get so caught in it.

01:02:51.380 --> 01:02:57.010 align:middle line:84%
There's just water
here, big, wet ocean.

01:02:57.010 --> 01:03:01.330 align:middle line:84%
So for a minute you're
like this, then you're not.

01:03:01.330 --> 01:03:04.120 align:middle line:90%
That's a life.

01:03:04.120 --> 01:03:07.700 align:middle line:84%
And even when I think I'm
a wave, I'm just ocean.

01:03:07.700 --> 01:03:13.690 align:middle line:84%
And this freed me to
go back to America

01:03:13.690 --> 01:03:18.270 align:middle line:84%
and really to be
able to sing 100%,

01:03:18.270 --> 01:03:21.020 align:middle line:84%
because it wasn't
about me, which

01:03:21.020 --> 01:03:26.170 align:middle line:84%
is what I had been longing
for to be free to sing,

01:03:26.170 --> 01:03:28.290 align:middle line:90%
to not be in my own way.

01:03:28.290 --> 01:03:31.200 align:middle line:84%
And now, for the
first time in my life,

01:03:31.200 --> 01:03:32.742 align:middle line:90%
I was out of my own way.

01:03:32.742 --> 01:03:35.400 align:middle line:90%


01:03:35.400 --> 01:03:38.936 align:middle line:84%
There was nobody
there to turn it off,

01:03:38.936 --> 01:03:44.560 align:middle line:84%
to push it away, to
turn the volume down,

01:03:44.560 --> 01:03:48.091 align:middle line:90%
to protect themself from.

01:03:48.091 --> 01:03:49.590 align:middle line:84%
There was just this
love everywhere.

01:03:49.590 --> 01:03:54.010 align:middle line:90%
[SONG  - "HARE KRISHNA"]

01:03:54.010 --> 01:04:06.510 align:middle line:90%


01:04:06.510 --> 01:04:11.951 align:middle line:84%
I was freed from thinking
that I was doing this,

01:04:11.951 --> 01:04:15.860 align:middle line:84%
that I was the one chanting,
that it was my responsibility,

01:04:15.860 --> 01:04:19.230 align:middle line:90%
it wasn't about me at all.

01:04:19.230 --> 01:04:21.440 align:middle line:84%
And the people
who were attracted

01:04:21.440 --> 01:04:24.920 align:middle line:84%
to me and to the chanting,
and coming towards that,

01:04:24.920 --> 01:04:27.630 align:middle line:84%
they might think they
were attracted to me,

01:04:27.630 --> 01:04:29.520 align:middle line:84%
