it personally how

01:04:58.385 --> 01:05:01.970 align:middle line:84%
it would allow me
to keep letting

01:05:01.970 --> 01:05:04.890 align:middle line:84%
go of the stuff that
pulled me out of myself

01:05:04.890 --> 01:05:08.610 align:middle line:84%
and bring me back to that place
that I had been in, back, out,

01:05:08.610 --> 01:05:13.060 align:middle line:84%
and back, out and back,
over, and over, and over.

01:05:13.060 --> 01:05:15.980 align:middle line:84%
But the chanting was
a way to come back.

01:05:15.980 --> 01:05:18.490 align:middle line:84%
All that shit they write
in the books is true.

01:05:18.490 --> 01:05:20.380 align:middle line:90%
Can you imagine that?

