The whole room becomes
him, that's what happens.

01:05:55.862 --> 01:05:58.540 align:middle line:90%


01:05:58.540 --> 01:06:02.087 align:middle line:84%
And the outer edges of
who we think we are just

01:06:02.087 --> 01:06:02.670 align:middle line:90%
dissolve then.

